### Health check (schema-aware readiness)
GET http://localhost:8080/healthz

###
### Create API key (admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/api-keys
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "http-client-demo",
  "max_concurrent_runs": 5,
  "max_requests_per_min": 60
}

###
### Create run with integer priority (valid)
POST http://localhost:8080/runs
Authorization: Bearer {{API_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json
Idempotency-Key: run-http-demo-001

{
  "template_name": "default",
  "priority": 10,
  "webhook_url": "https://example.com/webhook"
}

###
### Create run with string priority (invalid, expects 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/runs
Authorization: Bearer {{API_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "template_name": "default",
  "priority": "normal"
}
